.TH runner-why 1  "runner 0.12.0" "Runner Manual"
.SH NAME
runner\-why \- Explain how a specific task would dispatch (sources + PM trace)
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBrunner\-why\fR [\fB\-\-json\fR] [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] <\fITASK\fR> 
.SH DESCRIPTION
Explain how a specific task would dispatch (sources + PM trace)
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-\-json\fR
Emit JSON instead of human\-readable output
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help
.TP
<\fITASK\fR>
Task name to analyze
